meanings: Rookie. An actor or idol group who have just debuted in the entertainment industry. The rookie title doesn't just vanish after a year to so of working. The title will only drop once an actor or idol has achieved a certain level of success in the industry.
a new figure[face] in the literary world
reinforce a team with new players
